@startuml Hotel Reservation - State Diagram

[*] --> New : Guest creates reservation

New --> PendingPayment : Room selected
PendingPayment --> Confirmed : Payment successful
PendingPayment --> Cancelled : Payment failed / timeout

Confirmed --> CheckedIn : Guest arrives and checks in
Confirmed --> NoShow : Guest doesn't arrive
Confirmed --> Cancelled : Guest cancels before arrival

CheckedIn --> Active : Guest occupying room
Active --> CheckedOut : Guest checks out

CheckedOut --> Completed : Bill settled
NoShow --> Cancelled : No-show fee charged

Cancelled --> Refunded : Process refund (if applicable)
Completed --> Reviewed : Guest submits review

Refunded --> [*]
Reviewed --> [*]
Completed --> [*]

@enduml
